Inspect the repository and identify, when possible:

- primary programming language(s),
- package manager(s),
- build system(s),
- test framework(s),
- lint / format / typecheck tools,
- project type (library, CLI, API, service, web app, firmware, monorepo, hybrid, etc.),
- important entrypoints,
- important scripts,
- environment configuration,
- CI / automation clues,
