It should usually include:

- project overview,
- real stack and tooling,
- repo map,
- development workflow,
- validation checklist,
- code and documentation rules,
- open-questions workflow,
- high-risk areas,
- important reference files.

Do not leave generic bootstrap text in the final `AGENTS.md`.

If the repository already has a good `AGENTS.md`, improve it instead of replacing it unnecessarily.

